Mr Youth is seeking a team of motivated and creative college students to be a part of our exclusive network of young leaders. The Mr Youth Network will focus on using creative, strategic and analytic intel to inspire and fuel advocacy and action on campus.</p>
<p>
Members of the Mr Youth Network will learn critical business skills related to social media and word-of-mouth marketing while developing a powerful network of executives and peers that will last them throughout their professional career. Most importantly the Mr. Youth Network provides top-notch experience helping global brands develop and pioneer the future of youth marketing.</p>
